      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition, showing it has been well-cared for and is ready for many more miles. With a clean interior and a smooth, reliable performance, it offers a wonderful balance of quality and value for its next owner. It's a solid, dependable choice that you'll be proud to park in your driveway!",
